{
  "texts": [
    "-AI practitioner- [G7].",
    "In this study, the term \"clients\" denoted the people who commissioned their AI projects and they defined \"clients\" as follows, \"We refer to clients as those who commission and oversee AI projects, but do not do the technical work themselves\" [G7].",
    "Likewise, a participant in [G5] also shared similar thoughts and said users don't want to listen to ethics-related stuff as they don't understand it.",
    "The participant in [G5] said, ɓ \"Nobody wants to listen to ethics-related technical stuff.",
    "It's not relevant to the users.\""
  ]
}